Data Structure
Data structure is the answer to the questions on how we can maintain data and query them efficiently. 
- We might need some queries 
- Our algorithms might need some querying 

Each data structure is designed to handle some type of data

Mastery in data structure 
1. Wide knowledge of data structure and its purpose 
2. Know how to modify data structures to answer queries
3. able to formulate what kind of queries our our algorthm needs

Well known data structure 
1. Array / Vector 
Designed for accessing elements by index
2. Linked List / Stack / Queue
Designed to be a dynamic list
can only access the head/top/tail/top/front
3. Priority Queue / Heap
Designed to find the maximum / minimum
Can only access maximum / minimum data
4. Balanced Binary Tree / Hash Table 
Designed for CRUD (Create, Read, Update ,Delete)

